data.description:
Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath house on a corner lot in the Warren School District. It has a full basement and comes with a gazebo for great outdoor entertainment, and an extra wall oven in the kitchen for those big family get togethers. It has a 2 car garage and a large 48x24 building with concrete floor, electric and drain. Minutes to a boat ramp and fishing at Little Hocking Park. The house does come with multiple amenities including washer, dryer, refrigerator and dishwasher. Motivated sellers due to job relocation! Sellers will pay up to $5,000.00 towards closing costs.

***************SELLERS WILL PAY UP TO $5000.00 OF BUYERS CLOSING COSTS, POINTS AND PRE-PAID ITEMS!!!!!!!!**********************House is back on the market. No fault of seller or house.
